Fast food in America has lost everything that once made it exciting.. it’s no longer cheap, fast, or fun. The colorful, family-friendly restaurants of the past have been replaced with gray boxes serving overpriced slop. This video uncovers how the industry got here, and why eating fast food today feels more depressing than ever.
